object.text: Get their award winning beef noodle soup and some green onion pancake
The sesame wine pork liver soup and the fatty pork rice is what I crave every time I visit Taiwan and this is the spot.
The friend noodles are hand made and have a beautiful eggy flavor, with the noodles fried with the egg. Noodles have a soft chewy texture which is very delicious.
Quite easily the best restaurant in the xindian area.

list.name: Taiwan - Must Eats & Drinks
list.description: It'd be a shame to not check out these places if you're in town.

list.name: Taiwan - Should Eats
list.description: You should make a point of prioritizing these places when looking for places to eat, especially if you're in the area!

list.name: Eat Your Heart Out, TPE Edition
list.description: All the food I love to eat, 2015-6.

venue.name: 豐盛食堂 Feng Cheng Restaurant

object.text: Very good for family and friend gathering. Nice Taiwanese cuisine.

location.address: 新北市板橋區雙十路二段209號

object.text: 蝦鬆蝦鬆蝦鬆！love fried minced shrimp here!
The food is tasty, it's said that the chef used to cook for Chiang Kai Shek.
Excellent Taiwanese food in a sit down environment.  Don't forget to order mochi dessert
Amazing dim sum! Reservations are hard to get so call well in advance!
Only 130 nt for 8 pieces of soup dumplings. Worth it! Also get their house special potstickers.
Tradition Taiwanese breakfast, brunch, lunch, snack, dinner, and/or supper. Order their rice noodle soup and varieties of side dishes, such as stewed tofu, sliced pork, and greens. So good.
Very authentic place despite its aged setting n environment. Excellent xiaolongbao (steamed buns) n amazing pan-fried prune paste cake. Cabbage (baizai) salad is best in town.
Long line, worth the wait. Abalone is best...
Very delicious hotpot!!! Must try in Taipei!
I can only say delicious.
簡單就是美味，萬華的古早味名店
Great view!! Food was delicious as well. The noodle dish was really special. Located on the second floor so it is easy to miss
The goose meat is really worth trying while you cannot miss the mince belly pork in sauce with rice. The marinated spicy toofu is also my favorite. Highly recommend even you drop in by yourself.

venue.name: 莫宰羊羊肉料理專賣（大安台大店）

object.text: the soup is delicious. lamb and beef is quite fresh. the Chinese name of some dishes are quite funny :)

venue.name: 阿城鵝肉 土城總店

object.text: 還不錯吃，當地美食小吃
smoked oilfish(cod), steamed grouper are superb....but majority of their dishes are heavy and greasy.
肉類料理都很不錯，又嫩又入味。便當好貴。
Great atmosphere, relaxing, same for the cuisine presentation! Only disappointment is the speed of servings was a little hurried through, ironically unable to relax in such a relaxing environment!
Beautiful view! Lovely people and nice local food ^^!

venue.name: 馬辣頂級麻辣鴛鴦火鍋

object.text: The best all-you-can-eat spicy hotpot place!
Very tasty Xiao Long Bao and Fried Rice with Shredded Pork. Cozy ambience. Friendly staff and owner. A must not miss place to eat in Taipei! 😍
吻仔魚蛋炒飯90元，沒有很好吃

venue.name: 吉品海鮮餐廳 Ji Pin Restaurant

object.text: Ask for Candy for free deserts!
Spice beef noodles FTW! Make sure to order spicy!

venue.name: Daxi Old Street
venue.canonicalName: 大溪老街 Daxi Old Street

object.text: 統治時代のバロック式の建物が連なる美しい街並みと露店グルメ！煎鳥蛋(うずらの玉子を油に落として素揚げしたもの)と大渓の特産である豆干が美味しかったです！露店は週末に行ったほうが楽しめるようですね。
Homey Shanghai-nese cuisine.
Lovely Taiwanese kitchen, the sesame noodles 麻醬麵 were very tasty. Prices also very fair, also good for a quick meal
authentic taiwanese food with an amazing view from the 85th floor of taipei 101
Must not miss: 椒麻雞!!!! The BEST and my all-time favorite!
One of the best shanghai food restaurants in New Taipei City.
Knife cut noodles (刀削麵), 炸醬麵，beef noodle soup (牛肉麵)
Family owned restaurant serving local Beef Noodle Soup. The beef broth provides a deep umami flavour to get you all warm inside. Don't forget the dumplings in chili oil as a side dish - delicious!
The dry noodle with coconut milk sauce is so good! It comes with either chicken or beef.
價格平實份量足的平民美食，它的湯很大碗
nice place to eat and chat with Chef

location.address: 桃園縣中壢市民權路65號

object.text: Nice food and noodles
There is no cht cell reception here.
Great dumplings! Sit down to eat as they aren't very good as takeaway once they cool down
really great, although a little on the pricy side if you get a lot of dumplings...
Spicy peanut noodles and spicy wonton.. delicious
Traditional Taiwanese -- recommend the butternut squash tofu and shrimp, the small oysters, and the pork knuckle.
Their chicken stew is so strong and side dish, such as fired chicken and X.O. Fired rice are so good as well.
Get the lion head, and for dinner, always make reservations.
Beef roll and spicy wontons are great
won't visit again
Authentic and delicious Chinese cuisine
Ok as a backup. Meat pies are good (肉餡餅）but the soy milk 豆漿 was a bit burnt
Dumpling is its must try because it's what the restaurant is named after.  Chinese cabbage and pork fondue is what I don't expect to see here but this one add another must-try on the menu.
Beef tomato noodle soup is a great deal. Also, their 空心菜 is only $NT 90. Tasty food for an affordable price.

venue.name: 阿婆壽司 A Pou ShouSi

object.text: Good to eat
Xiao long bao, steamed dumpling, fried rice and hot n sour soup are a must in Taipei, Taiwan
+4 other mentions
Funky and modern yet capturing the true essence of Chinese cuisine. Amazing food experience.
Delicious oyster and intestine mee sua with special vinegar and chilli to accompany the dish. Definitely worth the trip. NTD 65 for large bowl.
Beef tendon and noodles in soup and beef wrapped in Chinese pancake
Dimsum was definitely amazing, the taste, way better than the branches in Seoul. The place is always packed with people. Great place to stop by if you're going to the observatory.
+34 other mentions
Chewy noodles in spicy soup with tender sliced beef, duck maroon jelly, garlic sprouts, green onion...It's not traditional beef noodle and is worth a try. The side dishes are also very tasty.
這道『金莎黃金豆腐』超推！沒點等於沒來了了^^
Crispy Chicken is good. Egg white with seafood source is fantastic. A good restaurant must try.
dumplings in beef soup is a must eat
Rice noodles with very special soup, people who like hot, spicy &sour dishes would love it.
配菜是無聊的鹹菜和無味的水煮高麗菜，淋醬是甜鹹口味，主角三寶不難吃也沒好吃到像似傳聞中的盛名。下回光顧的心情：真的沒有什麼好吃的時候，而他們店剛好還開著！
味道還不錯哦！
粥、麵、飯俱有獨到之處，店面雖然髒亂了點，但口味確實不俗。
l like dimsum. And I always visit CHAI797 in korea. But Kaochi is awesome like CHAI797. Great
+17 other mentions
My favorite tea time food
在地名店
Dumpling is good, fried rice is excellent, noodle soup is awesome. A very small but far more crowded restaurant. Open3 hours per day, and closed on weekend.
山東燒雞必點菜！大推！
One of the best beef noodles in town, mostly known to the locals than tourists. And there is always a line! Try the dried tofu too!
Best fried chicken I've ever eaten. Liked the soup dumplings more than Din Tai Fung. English menu available upstairs
Lively, informal atmosphere- food is fresh and delicious and cheap!  Try the steamed clams, the grilled prawns and chicken fried rice. There are photos of the food available for non-Chinese speakers
Different region DTF have different appetizers. Must order bamboo shoot with Asian mayo in Taiwan. It will bring that nice cool breeze in summer. Also, must order spicy and sour soup with your buns!

venue.name: 品鱻生猛活海鮮 Pinxian Seafood Restaurant

object.text: I enjoyed the Japanese lobster salad and the black pepper oyster tofu, but was spicy as hell
Delicious Cantonese dim sum, a branch from Hong Kong Michelin restaurant
小籠包が8個100元で食べられる  肉が美味しい
People compare it with DTF. This place is different, tho. More like a Chinese food joint. Quality of dumplings just average. Poor service.
+3 other mentions
香港スタイルの喫茶・軽食のお店。サンドイッチも「三明治」ではなく香港式表記である「三文治」。値段も安く、場所柄も手伝って若い人が多い。メニューの「本店特色」に上がっている蘿蔔糕 (大根もち)、腸粉、薄餅はどれも美味しいので、サイドメニューにお薦め。公仔麺はインスタントラーメン。
可以點例湯來喝。今天是花生雞爪湯，大概有6-8隻雞爪在裡面。
Traditional Taiwanese breakfast -- less of a line than Fu Hang. Some of my favorites are their soy milk (sweet or salty), Saobing with egg, danbing (egg pancake), and fantuan (Chinese rice burrito)

location.address: 中華路二段307巷（南機場夜市入口處）

object.text: Super long line.  It's 80NT for the chicken rice, which is somewhat similar to hainan chicken with soy sauce.  Comes with soup and some sides.
排隊名店。肥瘦比例恰好，味道鹹中帶甜還有酒香。一堆人開車騎車過來買，然後站在路邊吃完一根才離開。
Outstanding Chinese food. I've never eaten anything like it. Sadly, there is no English menu, and the staff doesn't speak English, but they are very helpful and will try to recommend something.
Tang Bao dumplings, beef burritos are very good .....
Try the house dish chicken soup with abalone.
The fried chicken broth is so good. FRIED. CHICKEN. BROTH.
Truly authentic
Great place to grab a bit since it open 24 hrs. Most of the foods are good, try black tea with soybean milk, my favorite!
Soy milk brekkie
Great variety of dishes incl vegetarian section! Usually crowded late nites. Go next door fr fresh soyabean drink after porridge!
rice rolls filled with delicious things for breakfast
The beef rice is good! Should try the vermicelli as well! Definitely the place to go before or after visiting Chiang Kai Shek Memorial Hall
Get the yam congee instead of plain white rice to go with the home-style Chinese dishes served here.
The Tan Tsi are a must I like the signature and the fat rice noodle version the best...rice with simmered pork is also brilliant and you can buy the pork as a souvenir.
